1.we can achive is-A relation ship by inheritance;
and has-A relationship by make class isnide the class or making a insatance variable of a
a calss those we want to establish has-A relationship;

example of has-A relationship-

class person{
class Address{
String address;
}
String Name;
}

form above example we can say person has A address not person is A address;

example of is-A realationship-

class Bird{
public void speek(){
  sysout("bird can speek");
}
}

class Parrot extend Bird{
public void speek(){
  sysout("parrot can speek like human");//overriding of methid of parrent class
}
}

from above example we can say parrot is A bird we can not say parrot has A bird;